<lb ed="X" n="0120c11"/><lb ed="R106" n="0057b08"/><row><cell>　右<note place="inline">某</note>輙以今晚就<g ref="#CB05903">𥨊</g>堂點茶特為伏望　尊慈特</cell></row>
